s (SSD) and the normalized cross-correlation\n(NCC), respectively with both a hard and a soft version of the\nincompressibility constraint.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Apr 2018 09:09:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-23"}
